data.description: PRIVATE, UPDATED & SPACIOUS HOME ON 10 ACRES!  Unveil the perfect blend of comfort and opportunity in this rural gem located just 138 miles from Atlanta! Nestled on 9.71 acres of cleared, flat land, this charming home is a dream come true for both families and entrepreneurs. Imagine family gatherings on the sprawling wraparound porch or exploring endless outdoor activities on this expansive property. With zoning that permits grazing, paddocks, and barns, it's an equestrian enthusiast's paradise. Whether you're envisioning a peaceful family haven or pursuing your entrepreneurial dreams with horses or hobby farming, the time to act is now. Don't miss out on this unique chance to embrace nature and modern living. Schedule your viewing today and seize the endless possibilities that await!". This home features a bedroom on the main, plus 4 more upstairs. 3 renovated baths, granite and stainless kitchen, hardwoods, fireplace, attached garage and more.  Contact us directly for a private tour. Virtual Tour: youtube/watch?v=yF-zDyep6p0
